{"tid":2296488,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD 開放 SAM 技術給 NVIDIA INTEL 最終 AU + N卡、IU + A 卡都能加速 !!","createTime":"2020-11-22T13:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T04:51:17.000Z","uid":28114,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"83c725982a00b075ca91b5ee137e74acd50749f9","tid":2296488,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/11/source/2113491959343080697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F11%2Fsource%2F2113491959343080697.jpg&h=fc74f132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAMD 剛發佈最新 Radeon RX 6800 系列新卡，其中一項新技術稱為 SAM (Smart Access Memory) 技術，可以令 CPU 能完全存取 GPU 的顯示記憶體，無需再透過 Windows 的映射進行進行資料交換，但暫時只限於 A 卡配 AU，不過 AMD 昨日透露正與 NVIDIA 及 Intel 討論，期望可以開放 SAM 技術讓不同 CPU、不同 GPU 都能使用。<br />\n <br />\n傳統的 x86 PC 架構中受限於 PCIe 規範，只能透過 Base Address Register (BAR) 每次將 256MB 系統記憶體射映到 GPU 記憶體，這個限制嚴重影響到系統記憶體與 GPU 記憶體之間的資料傳輸效率。<br />\n <br />\nAMD 在 RDNA 2 中加入了全新 Smart Access Memory 技術，當用家使用AMD 新一代 Ryzen 5000 系列處理器時，不再使用 PCIe Mapping 方式，CPU 可以直接存取 GPU 記憶體，完全解除 CPU 與 GPU 之間的讀寫瓶頸，遊戲性能平均能提升約 6%，尤其對大量使用 Texture 貼圖的遊戲，效能提升會更為明顯。<br />\n <br />\n昨日 AMD 副總裁暨 Radeon 事業群 Scott Herkelman 透過，在 SAM 技術正與 NVIDIA 進行討論，讓 AMD CPU 搭配 NVIDIA 顯示卡時亦可以使用 SAM，同時亦向 Intel 提出開放 SAM 技術的意願，未來很大機會不論任何 CPU 配任何卡都能啟動，不再局限於某個平台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19918/AMD_開放_SAM_技術給_NVIDIA_INTEL_最終_AU_%2B__N卡IU_%2B_A_卡都能加速_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19918%2FAMD_%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE_SAM_%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%B5%A6_NVIDIA_INTEL_%E6%9C%80%E7%B5%82_AU_%252B__N%E5%8D%A1IU_%252B_A_%E5%8D%A1%E9%83%BD%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F_&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT6Fdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=505ee01f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19918/AMD_開放_SAM_技術給_NVIDIA_INTEL_最終_AU_%2B__N卡IU_%2B_A_卡都能加速_</a>"},{"pid":"726dbe65f0506d7b9289c5a6fbfa0071f6e13973","tid":2296488,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:40:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">AMD YES</span></span>"},{"pid":"896881ed4c34e43b09ffeb1e76243ecd179b658f","tid":2296488,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"到AMD擠牙膏"},{"pid":"8bfbffd106c1996dde7d32896dba94e66d4b0546","tid":2296488,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"896881ed4c34e43b09ffeb1e76243ecd179b658f","tid":2296488,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"到AMD擠牙膏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"都冇擠，一下子爆曬出嚟"},{"pid":"58461d822bff7e6fedc4da314fb02706a7f888d1","tid":2296488,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"不過 AMD 昨日透露正與 NVIDIA 及 Intel 討論，戇尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c064c429ad517c4dd718d108427d509f6105ad0","tid":2296488,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96dca7383a58fb4ff72b81430a39bcc1e3eb8545","tid":2296488,"uid":169071,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"唔好話我馬後炮，一早諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣心諗cuda個D display ram同mother board ram Map黎map去都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢樣技術應該AMD出console個陣諗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306c6c6cff17f391636be8b8c291abc7bede6225","tid":2296488,"uid":244958,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:33:05.000Z","msg":"開放技術，其實係雙贏"},{"pid":"fe539c99449149283da52ea458328b83fa80f93c","tid":2296488,"uid":43066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-